      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers straightforward transportation value for the right buyer. A practical option for someone seeking an inexpensive car with usable life left, it presents an opportunity to get on the road without a major upfront cost. Sold as-is and reflected in the price, this is a sensible choice for buyers who prioritize affordability and potential over perfection.",
