      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels that won\u2019t break the bank? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward, honest option for someone who needs basic transport, a project, or a handy runabout. It\u2019s priced fairly for what it is and could be a great fit for the right buyer who appreciates value and a bit of potential. If you want something cheap, usable, and worth a look, send me a message.",
